          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="#" target="_blank" class="flex-1 w-full">
          <Button>Buy Your SOLPAKA</Button>
        </a>
        <a href="#" target="_blank" class="flex-1 w-full">
          <Button>View Charts</Button>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div>
